ating_scandal\">{{Cite web | title = The great university cheating scandal | website=macleans.ca| publisher = Macleans | year = 2007 | accessdate = May 9, 2014 | url = http://www.macleans.ca/general/the-great-university-cheating-scandal/}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"cheating_students\">{{Cite web | title = Cheating students punished by the 1000s, but many more go undetected | website=cbc.ca| publisher = CBC | year = 2014 | accessdate = May 9, 2014 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/cheating-students-punished-by-the-1000s-but-many-more-go-undetected-1.2549621}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"cheating_international_students\">{{Cite web | title = Why many international students get a failing grade in academic integrity | website=theglobeandmail.com| publisher = The Globe and Mail | year = 2011  |accessdate = May 9, 2014 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/cheating-students-punished-by-the-1000s-but-many-more-go-undetected-1.2549621}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"corrupt_to_the_core\">{{Cite web | title = Book Review: Corrupt to the Core | website=preventcancernow.ca| publisher = Prevent Cancer Now | year = 2011  |accessdate = May 9, 2014 | url = http://www.preventcancernow.ca/book-review-corrupt-to-the-core}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"rcmp_corruption_study\">{{Cite web | title = RCMP study finds 322 incidents of corruption within force during 11-year period| website=ottawacitizen.com| publisher = Ottawa Citizen | year = 2014  |accessdate = May 19, 2014 | url = https://ottawacitizen.com/news/RCMP+study+finds+incidents+corruption+within+national/9854635/story.html}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"rcmp_corruption\">{{Cite web | title = RCMP failed to track internal misconduct for years| website=cbc.ca | publisher = CBC | year = 2013  |accessdate = May 19, 2014 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/rcmp-failed-to-track-internal-misconduct-for-years-1.1353537}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"rcmp_sexual_assult\">{{Cite web | title = 282 join RCMP sexual harassment class-action lawsuit | website=cbc.ca | publisher = CBC | year = 2013  |accessdate = May 19, 2014 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/282-join-rcmp-sexual-harassment-class-action-lawsuit-1.1346440}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"psc\">{{Cite web | title = The 100 years of the Public Service Commission of Canada 1908\u20132008 | website=psc-cfp.gc.ca | publisher = Public Service Commission of Canada | year = 2008  |accessdate = June 6, 2014 | url = http://www.psc-cfp.gc.ca/abt-aps/tpsc-hcfp/hist-eng.htm}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"independence_of_public_service_study\">{{Cite web  | title = The Puzzle of Independence for Administrative Bodies  | website = law.yale.edu  | publisher = Yale Law School  | year = 2008  | accessdate = June 6, 2014  | url = http://www.law.yale.edu/documents/pdf/CompAdminLaw/Lorne_Sossin_CompAdLaw_paper.pdf  | url-status = dead  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619035433/http://www.law.yale.edu/documents/pdf/CompAdminLaw/Lorne_Sossin_CompAdLaw_paper.pdf  | archivedate = June 19, 2010  | df = mdy-all  }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"csis_overseer_abolished\">{{Cite web | title = Ottawa abolishes spy overseer's office | website=nationalpost.com | publisher = National Post | year = 2012  |accessdate = June 6, 2014 | url = http://news.nationalpost.com/2012/04/26/csis-office-of-the-inspector-general/}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"access_to_information_blocked\">{{Cite web | title = Canadians' rightful access to public information being blocked, experts say | website=thestar.com | publisher = The Toronto Star | year = 2014  |accessdate = June 6, 2014 | url = https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2014/04/27/canadians_rightful_access_to_public_information_being_blocked_experts_say.html}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"tories_intefer_with_right_to_information\">{{Cite news | title = Three Tory staffers interfered in releasing government information, watchdog says | website=theglobeandmail.com | publisher = The Globe and Mail | year = 2014  |accessdate = June 6, 2014 | url = https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/three-tory-staffers-interfered-in-releasing-government-information-watchdog-says/article17914868/}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"best_practices\">{{Cite web | title = \"Best Practices to Fight Corruption\" Canada: Selected Programs - The Government of Canada  | website=unodc.org | publisher = UNODC  |accessdate = June 6, 2014 | url = https://www.unodc.org/documents/corruption/Best%20Practices/Canada%20Best%20Practices%20to%20Fight%20Corruption.pdf}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"conflick_of_interest\">{{Cite web|title=Conflict of Interest|publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia|date=December 15, 2013|url=https://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/conflict-of-interest|accessdate=September 6, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"FNFTA\">{{Cite web | title = Chief, ex-wife of small B.C. First Nations band pocket $200K in tax-free salaries  | website=calgarysun.ca | publisher = The Calgary Sun | year = 2014  |accessdate = November 5, 2014 | url = http://www.calgarysun.com/2014/11/03/chief-ex-wife-of-small-bc-first-nations-band-pocket-200k-in-tax-free-salaries}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"conflict-of-interest\">{{Cite web | title = Conservative minister Diane Finley broke conflict-of-interest rules funding Toronto-area group: ethics watchdog | website=nationalpost.com | publisher = PostMedia News | year = 2015 |accessdate = March 10, 2015 | url = http://news.nationalpost.com/2015/03/10/conservative-minister-diane-finley-broke-conflict-of-interest-rules-funding-toronto-area-group-ethics-watchdog/}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ontario_police_union_corruption\">{{Cite web | title = OPP union leaders stole and laundered funds, RCMP allege| website=cbc.ca | publisher = CBC | year = 2015 |accessdate = March 19, 2015 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/opp-union-leaders-stole-and-laundered-funds-rcmp-allege-1.2994229}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ontari_election_bribery\">{{Cite web | title = Ontario politics hits rock bottom with byelection allegations | website=torontosun.com| publisher = Toronto Sun | year = 2015 |accessdate = March 19, 2015 | url =http://www.torontosun.com/2015/02/19/ontario-politics-hits-rock-bottom-with-byelection-allegations}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ibm_ebr_arrests\">{{Cite web | title = Seven arrests in $24M Revenue Quebec contract fraud: Cops | website=torontosun.com| publisher = Toronto Sun | year = 2015 |accessdate = March 19, 2015 | url =http://www.torontosun.com/2015/03/11/six-arrests-in-24m-revenue-quebec-contract-fraud-cops}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"quebec_it_fraud\">{{Cite web | title = Seven arrests in $24M Revenue Quebec contract fraud: Cops | website=theobserver.ca| publisher = The Observer | year = 2015 |accessdate = March 19, 2015 | url =http://www.theobserver.ca/2015/03/11/six-arrests-in-24m-revenue-quebec-contract-fraud-cops}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"integrity_regime\">{{Cite web | title = Government of Canada's Integrity Regime | website=www.tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca| publisher = Government of Canada | year = 2015 |accessdate = October 23, 2015 | url =http://www.tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca/ci-if/ci-if-eng.html}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ontario_liberal_party_bribery_scandal\">{{Cite news | title = Alleged Ontario Liberal bribery scandal shines light on world of political patronage  | website=theglobeandmail.com| publisher = The Globe and Mail | year = 2015 |accessdate = October 23, 2015 | url = https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/liberal-fundraiser-faces-charges-in-alleged-by-election-bribery-scandal/article26514410/}}</ref>\n<!-- unused refs <ref>{{Cite web | title = Kelly McParland: 'Corrupt' is the word to describe Ontario government's ties to teachers' unions | website=nationalpost.com| publisher = National Post | year = 2015 |accessdate = October 27, 2015 | url = http://news.nationalpost.com/full-comment/kelly-mcparland-corrupt-is-the-only-word-to-describe-ontario-governments-ties-to-teachers-unions}}</ref>\n<ref>{{Cite news | title = Ontario government's payments to teacher unions top $3.7-million | website=theglobeandmail.com| publisher = The Globe and Mail | 