 for Reforestation and the Protection of Natural Habitats)\n* \"S\u00fcrg\u00fcn A\u015fk\u0131m\u0131z\" (1999) \u2013 [[Hazal]]'s song, performed by Karaca in 10th Alt\u0131n G\u00fcvercin Song Contest.\n* \"Bir Yudum Hayat\" (2000) \u2013 Performed in 11th Alt\u0131n G\u00fcvercin Song Contest.\n* \"Bir K\u0131r\u0131k Sevda\" (2000) \u2013 Performed in Turkey pre-eliminations of [[Eurovision Song Contest]]\n* \"G\u00f6rev Ba\u015f\u0131nday\u0131z\" (I\u015f\u0131n Karaca & [[\u00d6zcan Deniz]] feat. The Veleds) (2005) \u2013 A special song for celebration of 160th year of Police Department of Turkey.\n* \"Unutama Beni\" (2008) \u2013 Cover version of [[Esmeray]]'s hit for [[ATV Turkey|ATV]]'s 2008 TV series \"Elif\" as theme song.\n* \"\u00c7anakkale T\u00fcrk\u00fcs\u00fc\" (with 16 other singers) (2013) \u2013 A special song for 98th anniversary of [[Naval operations in the Dardanelles Campaign#The Battle of March 18|Gallipoli Memorial Day]].<ref>{{cite web|title=17 Farkl\u0131 Sanat\u00e7\u0131dan \u00c7anakkale T\u00fcrk\u00fcs\u00fc Dinle - 2013|url=http://haberciniz.biz/17-farkli-sanatcidan-canakkale-turkusu-dinle-2013-1933799h.htm|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Music videos==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Song\n!Album\n!Director\n|-\n|2001\n|\"Tutunamad\u0131m\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Anadilim A\u015fk]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|K\u0131van\u00e7 Baru\u00f6n\u00fc\n|-\n|2002\n|\"[[Ba\u015fka Bahar]]\"\n|-\n|2003\n|\"Aram\u0131za Yollar\"\n|Waleed Nassif\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2004\n|\"Sen Gitttin mi Ben \u00d6l\u00fcr\u00fcm\"\n|[[O \u015eark\u0131lar]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Sessiz Kalma\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Sessiz Kalma\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Biray Dalk\u0131ran\n|-\n|\"Sessiz Kalma Remix\"\n|-\n|\"Yetinmeyi Bilir misin?\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[\u0130\u00e7inde A\u015fk Var]]\n|Altan D\u00f6nmez\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|2005\n|\"Bekleyelim de G\u00f6relim\"\n|\n|-\n|\"Ho\u015fg\u00f6r\u00fc\"\n|Korhan Bozkurt\n|-\n|\"G\u00f6rev Ba\u015f\u0131nday\u0131z\"\n|\n|O\u011fuzhan Tercan\n|-\n|-\n|r