ilim A\u015fk]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|K\u0131van\u00e7 Baru\u00f6n\u00fc\n|-\n|2002\n|\"[[Ba\u015fka Bahar]]\"\n|-\n|2003\n|\"Aram\u0131za Yollar\"\n|Waleed Nassif\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2004\n|\"Sen Gitttin mi Ben \u00d6l\u00fcr\u00fcm\"\n|[[O \u015eark\u0131lar]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Sessiz Kalma\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Sessiz Kalma\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Biray Dalk\u0131ran\n|-\n|\"Sessiz Kalma Remix\"\n|-\n|\"Yetinmeyi Bilir misin?\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[\u0130\u00e7inde A\u015fk Var]]\n|Altan D\u00f6nmez\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|2005\n|\"Bekleyelim de G\u00f6relim\"\n|\n|-\n|\"Ho\u015fg\u00f6r\u00fc\"\n|Korhan Bozkurt\n|-\n|\"G\u00f6rev Ba\u015f\u0131nday\u0131z\"\n|\n|O\u011fuzhan Tercan\n|-\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2006\n|\"Mandalinalar\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Ba\u015fka 33/3]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|Kubilay Kasap\n|-\n|\"Kalp Tanr\u0131ya Emanet\"\n|-\n|2007\n|\"B\u0131rakma\"\n|-\n| 2009\n| \"Bilmece\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Uyan\u0131\u015f (album)|Uyan\u0131\u015f]]\n| Erol Y\u0131lmaz\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"| 2010\n| \"Uyan\u0131\u015f\"\n| Sedat Do\u011fan & Cem Ba\u015feskio\u011flu<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.isinkaraca.com/isin-karaca/index.php/yeni-video-klip-uyanis-tum-tv-kanallarinda/ |title=Yeni video klip \"Uyan\u0131\u015f\" t\u00fcm tv kanallar\u0131nda. |publisher=isinkaraca.com |accessdate=2010-02-07 |language=Turkish }}{{Dead link|date=January 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n| \"K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 Ruj\" (with [[Berkant Akg\u00fcrgen|Berkant]])\n| Her Devrin Devleri\n| Ey\u00fcp Dirlik\n|-\n|-\n| \"Dert Bende Derman Sende\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[Arabesque: Ge\u00e7mi\u015f, Ge\u00e7memi\u015f Hi\u00e7...|Arabesque]]\n|rowspan=\"5\"| Sedat Do\u011fan <ref>{{Cite web| url = https://twitter.com/isinkaraja/status/10920721551 | title = twitter | accessdate = 2010-04-15 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.jetsetistanbul.com/altsayfa.asp?hbid=1472 | title = H\u00fcseyin Karaday\u0131 ikinci klibi \"E\u011flen G\u00fczelim\"e \u00e7ekti | accessdate = 2010-08-11 }}</ref><r